msgid "Protected Virtualization on s390x"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../system/s390x/protvirt.rst:4
msgid ""
"The memory and most of the registers of Protected Virtual Machines (PVMs) "
"are encrypted or inaccessible to the hypervisor, effectively prohibiting VM "
"introspection when the VM is running. At rest, PVMs are encrypted and can "
"only be decrypted by the firmware, represented by an entity called "
"Ultravisor, of specific IBM Z machines."
msgstr ""

